<h1>Birthday Parties</h1>
<h3>
    Looking for a cool and fun place to have your child's birthday party?
    Give that special child a truly unique day at Big Joel's Safari!
</h3>

<div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1">
                    What's included in our Safari Birthday Package
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li>Admission for 10 kids and 10 adults to Big Joel's Safari.</li>
                    <li>Additional guests must pay the standard park entree fee.</li>
                    <li>Free admission for the birthday child's parents and up to four Grandparents.</li>
                    <li>Each kids will recieve a small souvenir feed cup with animal feed for the animals.</li>
                    <li>Party guests have private access to the Safari Party Room for 2 hours, with 30 additional minutes for prep time beforehand.</li>
                    <li>The party room has Safari themed decorations and is climate controlled.</li>
                    <li>Basic cups, plates, napkins, and utensils are provided.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
