                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <h4>We encourage our guests go over the rules before their party.</h4>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li>All guests must check in at the front desk before entering the park.</li>
                    <li>Guests are permitted to bring food and drink into the party room. Alchohol is prohibited.</li>
                    <li>All food and drink must stay in the party room for the safety of our animals.</li>
                    <li>Guests are permitted to bring balloons and other party decorations.</li>
                    <li>Balloons and party favors, such as whistles are to stay in the party room.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
